PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 33 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in the PROVINCE OF QUEBEC which occured between March 28 and April 15, 1998, to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.
